thread.title: Charles Schlorf
thread.title_full: Mystery Tackle Box reviewed by Charles Schlorf

author: Charles Schlorf
title: Charles Schlorf
text: If you are an experienced fisherman these boxes can give you a surprise every month just for fun and even give you new items on the market to explore or try out. If you are beginning your fishing career or unsure if certain seasons these packages and tips can really help you locate fish. All around good product. Hopefully catch company continues making it a great product.
